```html
<!-- templates/monthlyVAT.hbs -->
<!-- This is a Handlebars HTML template for Monthly UAE VAT Summary report for FTA compliance -->

<!-- Include the necessary CSS and JS files -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/path/to/your/css/file.css">
<script src="/path/to/your/js/file.js"></script>

<!-- Start of the HTML body -->
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Monthly UAE VAT Summary Report</h1>
        
        <!-- Tenant TRN section -->
        <section id="tenant-trn">
            <h2>Tenant TRN: {{this.tenantTRN}}</h2>
        </section>

        <!-- VAT calculation summary table -->
        <section id="vat-summary">
            <h2>VAT Calculation Summary Table</h2>
            <table class="table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Category</th>
                        <th>Total Sales (AED)</th>
                        <th>VAT Rate (%)</th>
                        <th>VAT Amount (AED)</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each this.vatSummary}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{this.category}}</td>
                        <td>{{this.totalSales}}</td>
                        <td>{{this.vatRate}}</td>
                        <td>{{this.vatAmount}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </section>

        <!-- Weekly breakdown section -->
        <section id="weekly-breakdown">
            <h2>Weekly Breakdown</h2>
            <!-- Add your weekly breakdown content here -->
        </section>

        <!-- Sales by category section -->
        <section id="sales-by-category">
            <h2>Sales By Category</h2>
            <!-- Add your sales by category content here -->
        </section>

        <!-- Invoice list section -->
        <section id="invoice-list">
            <h2>Invoice List</h2>
            <!-- Add your invoice list content here -->
        </section>

        <!-- Declaration section -->
        <section id="declaration">
            <h2>Declaration</h2>
            <!-- Add your declaration content here -->
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
```
This is a basic template for the Monthly UAE VAT Summary report. You will need to replace `{{this.tenantTRN}}`, `{{#each this.vatSummary}}` with your actual data from MongoDB. Also, you may want to customize the CSS and JS files according to your needs.